            Please refer to our &lt;a href=&quot;#&quot; class=&quot;underline underline-offset-2 text-primary dark:text-primary-dark&quot;&gt;refund policy page&lt;/a&gt; for details.
        &lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/AccordionSection&gt;
&lt;/Accordion&gt;
                </CodeViewer>
            </section>

            <!-- Single Open Accordion (Only one section open) -->
            <section class="my-8 py-2">
                <Heading Level="HeadingLevel.H2" QuickReferenceTitle="Single Open Accordion" class="scroll-mt-20">
                    Single Open Accordion
                </Heading>
                <Paragraph>
                    In this example, <code>AllowMultipleOpen</code> is set to <code>false</code>, ensuring that only one section is open at a time.
                </Paragraph>

